&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2 x 37.5 hours Staff Nurse &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1x 24 hours Staff Nurse (maternity cover 6 months ) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to be part of a dynamic organisation, with an overall aim to deliver outstanding patient care? Do you have excellent clinical skills and a desire to further develop your knowledge and skill base?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic staff nurses who are passionate about delivering high standards of care , team player, excellent communicator with previous surgical experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newton 2 is a short stay elective surgery ward, we have recently increased our service to cater for various surgical specialties such as colorectal surgery level one , ophthalmology, Urology, ENT and general surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Surgery is a diverse and expanding service at SWB. Over the last twelve months the Trust has made significant investment across our wards, theatres and specialist services. The surgical service is an innovative and progressive group within the Trust, which will support you in expanding and growing your career pathways as well as creating opportunity for you in your clinical practice, leadership and management portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We recognise that outstanding nursing is fundamental to the delivery of the safest and highest quality patient care and therefore your commitment to us will be nurtured and reflected through your career journey at the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Staff benefits include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onsite free gym on both hospital sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Childcare facilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Car lease scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Savings with local supermarkets / national and local discounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Financial advice through Neyber&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsidised purchase schemes for new technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a really exciting time for our organisation, with the opening of a brand new hospital in the future and the continued evolution of the way we perform cutting edge medicine. We look forward to meeting you and inviting you to &lt;strong&gt;#bepartofsomethingamazing.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
